txt.en: 'Nineteen and Twenty!'
Deeping Wall - Solo
'Twenty-one! Getting tired yet Gimli?'
'That's six!'
'Twenty-two! I will need to find more arrows soon.'
'Seven! Eight!'
'Twenty-three as well! There will be many more before this night ends!'
'Eleven!'
'Twelve! Try to keep up Gimli!'
'Thirteen! Do you need me to take a break?'
Goblins are assaulting the centre towers! Protect the winch and any supplies within!
Orc defilers are coming to destroy the centre battlements. Destroy them and their foul totems!
<rgb=#FF0000>The defiler's totems have been destroyed!</rgb>
'Hanhar arrives on the wall!'
'Dajambat climbs to the top of the eastern tower!'
'MÃ¡bis assaults the ballista in the eastern tower!'
<rgb=#FF0000>The enemy has used the targeting banners to find their range on the wall!</rgb>
<rgb=#FF0000>The Rohirrim clearing the supplies have been defeated!</rgb>
<rgb=#00FF00>The bases of the towers have been protected!</rgb>
You must have completed the 'Helm's Dike' battle.
The enemy is beneath us sneaking through the culvert! Aid the workers in sealing the opening at once!
<rgb=#FF0000>The Shakh-hai overseers have been allowed to rampage through your defences!</rgb>
'Four!'
'Five!'
'Six! Arrows are cheating!'
<rgb=#FF0000>The totems have decimated the wall!</rgb>
Orc defilers are coming to destroy the battlements. Destroy them and their foul totems!
'Seven! Ha-ha!'
'What! You cannot just skip numbers!'
<rgb=#FF0000>The towers have been critically weakened!</rgb>
'Eight and nine! We are just getting started!'
'Ten! My axe hungers for more!'
Sappers have infiltrated the Deeping-coomb! Do not let their powder kegs damage the tower's base!
'Eleven and twelve! Both in one strike!'
<rgb=#FF0000>Your workers have been defeated, the culvert remains a weakness!</rgb>
<rgb=#00FF00>The culvert has been sealed!</rgb>
'Thirteen! They do not count if they're not on the wall!'
<rgb=#00FF00>The defiler and his totems have been destroyed!</rgb>
<rgb=#00FF00>The targeting banners have been kept from the wall!</rgb>
'Fourteen!'
<rgb=#00FF00>The Shakh-hai overseers have been defeated!</rgb>
'Prepare the catapult! Steel your resolve! They come!'
'Thirteen! They do not count if they're not on the wall!'
'Push over the ladders and cut down their hooks!'
<rgb=#FF0000>The door to the Hornburg has been destroyed!</rgb>
'Watch for sappers! Disarm any black powder!'
The east tower is under attack! Legolas and the Rohirrim labourers are in need of your aid.
'Load the rock drops and then thin their numbers!'
'Thirteen and a half!'
'Thirteen! Line them up!'
'Fourteen and a half!'
'Fifteen then!'
<rgb=#00FF00>Gimli has completed his patrol!</rgb>
'Twenty? Bah! Seventeen!'
'Ha! My axe will never tire! Nineteen!'
<rgb=#FF0000>The workers have been defeated. The tower's defences will have to stand as is!</rgb>
'Twenty-two! Twenty-three!'
The Orcs are planting targeting banners for their catapults. Tear them down before we suffer the consequences!
<rgb=#FF0000>The defiler has escaped!</rgb>
Goblins are assaulting the eastern tower! Protect the winch and the supplies within!
<rgb=#00FF00>The workers in the tower have been protected!</rgb>
<rgb=#FF0000>A winch has been destroyed!</rgb>
<rgb=#00FF00>The door to the Hornburg has been protected!</rgb>
Shakh-hai overseers have left their command posts and joined the chaos of the battle! Do not let them turn the battle!
'Twenty!'
'Fifteen, sixteen, seventeen!'
Gimli has gone to defeat the enemies that have crept into the Deeping-coomb! Join and aid him!
The door to the Hornburg is under attack! Protect the gate-house and the injured soldiers within.
'Eighteen!'
'Being half sized does not mean you can count half kills!'
<rgb=#00FF00>The winch and tower are secure!</rgb>
